Workflow Overview
Capture Packets:

Use tools like tcpdump or scapy to capture traffic in real-time or from a file.
Extract Features:

Use pyshark, scapy, or Wireshark to extract necessary features.
Preprocess Features:

Apply your preprocessing pipeline to transform the extracted data.
Model Inference:

Use the preprocessed data as input to your trained model to classify traffic.
Alert and Log:

If the model detects malicious activity, trigger alerts or log the results.